      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Observe them, men; their lives are a perpetual dance of base impulse, lacking the refinement of true society. Their attire, so rudimentary, speaks to a lack of self-control, while their customs reveal a primitive untidiness. They are vibrant, yes, but their existence is one of raw, unchanneled instinct, a state that requires the firm hand of European governance to elevate them.\"",
